OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of killing
OL,4,Ccellmate
OL,6,FA prisoner has been found guilty of
OL,7,Ffatally strangling his cellmate at HMP
OL,8,FBristol.
OL,10,FMichael Harkin, 35, was convicted of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,12,Fresponsibility following the death of
OL,13,FDan Childs in June 2023.
OL,15,FThe 38-year-old was found unresponsive
OL,16,Fin his cell on 5 June and died at the
OL,17,Fscene, Avon and Somerset Police said.
