OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of killing
OL,4,Ccellmate
OL,6,FHarkin was also found guilty of
OL,7,Fwounding a second prisoner, and was
OL,8,Fremanded in custody to be sentenced on
OL,9,F11 October during the hearing at
OL,10,FBristol Crown Court.
OL,12,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,13,FInspector Nadine Partridge said "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are foremost with the family
OL,15,Fof Dan Childs who have had their much-
OL,16,Floved son, brother and uncle taken
OL,17,Faway from them."
OL,19,FThe jury heard Harkin had two
OL,20,Fdifferent cellmates in the days
OL,21,Fleading up to Mr Child's death.
