OL,6,FThe first prisoner asked to moved to a
OL,7,Fdifferent cell on 1 June, after one
OL,8,Fday of sharing with Harkin.
OL,10,FHe later told police it was because
OL,11,F"there was something not right about"
OL,12,FHarkin.
OL,14,FStaff subsequently decided Mr Childs
OL,15,Fshould share that cell with Harkin
OL,16,Finstead.
