OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of killing
OL,4,Ccellmate
OL,6,FOn 5 June, police were called to HMP
OL,7,FBristol after Harkin assaulted his
OL,8,Fformer cellmate in the showers, using
OL,9,Fan improvised blade to wound the man
OL,10,Fin his face, shoulder, neck arms and
OL,11,Fleg.
OL,13,FFollowing the attack, prison staff
OL,14,Fchecked on Mr Childs and found him
OL,15,Funresponsive in his cell.
OL,17,FA post-mortem examination revealed he
OL,18,Fhad been fatally strangled with an
OL,19,Fitem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
