OL,3,CPrisoner found guilty of killing
OL,4,Ccellmate
OL,6,FCCTV footage reviewed during the Avon
OL,7,Fand Somerset Police murder
OL,8,Finvestigation found no other person
OL,9,Fentered Harkin and Mr Childs' cell
OL,10,Fprior to the doors being unlocked the
OL,11,Ffollowing morning, when Harkin walked
OL,12,Fto the showers.
OL,14,FA jury, having heard evidence from
OL,15,Fmedical experts during the course of
OL,16,Fthe 16-day trial, found Harkin not
OL,17,Fguilty of murder following a direction
OL,18,Fby the judge.
